WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 34=

01:49.340 --> 01:50.180
Commandant Wu,

01:50.830 --> 01:51.700
how is your injury?

01:52.860 --> 01:53.700
General,

01:54.390 --> 01:55.700
sorry I let you down.

02:01.630 --> 02:02.550
I've heard about it.

02:03.190 --> 02:04.470
What exactly happened there?

02:05.630 --> 02:06.470
At that time,

02:06.830 --> 02:07.750
Captain Meng and I

02:07.750 --> 02:09.140
were raiding their main forces

02:09.140 --> 02:10.700
according to your splitting strategy

02:10.700 --> 02:12.070
when we were nearly ambushed.

02:12.860 --> 02:14.390
Those Chong soldiers who attacked us

02:15.230 --> 02:16.070
were very weird.

02:16.830 --> 02:17.670
They seemed

02:18.270 --> 02:19.110
fearless of pain.

02:19.860 --> 02:20.700
What's worse,

02:20.990 --> 02:22.070
when we retreated,

02:22.070 --> 02:23.350
many enemy assassins

02:23.350 --> 02:24.230
suddenly appeared

02:24.230 --> 02:25.790
out of nowhere.

02:26.230 --> 02:27.990
We were caught

02:27.990 --> 02:29.790
completely off guard.

02:35.180 --> 02:36.420
The All-Knowing was there.

02:38.020 --> 02:38.860
What was our loss?

02:40.350 --> 02:41.900
By the time I realized the problem,

02:42.420 --> 02:44.110
we had lost 40 percent of our forces.

02:44.390 --> 02:45.700
I didn't dare to get bogged down,

02:46.140 --> 02:47.950
so I led our troops in retreat.

02:48.390 --> 02:49.230
Commandant Wu,

02:49.990 --> 02:51.300
the battlefield is unpredictable.

02:51.830 --> 02:52.790
You did well enough.

02:53.830 --> 02:54.670
I'll send scouts

02:54.860 --> 02:56.070
to find out what happened.

03:27.900 --> 03:29.420
When I offered you presents,

03:30.510 --> 03:32.230
you'd at least give them a good look.

03:35.830 --> 03:36.830
Now when I think of it,

03:37.460 --> 03:38.390
these common things

03:39.180 --> 03:40.550
really don't suit you.

04:01.110 --> 04:01.950
I've made you

04:01.950 --> 04:03.350
a queen's crown by myself.

04:05.300 --> 04:06.230
Won't you try it on?

04:07.350 --> 04:09.020
The one who wanted this crown

04:09.020 --> 04:10.900
was killed by you.

04:13.460 --> 04:15.180
Yan Zhang trained those puppet spirits

04:16.060 --> 04:17.470
for you, didn't she?

04:20.470 --> 04:22.060
She was completely devoted to you.

04:23.300 --> 04:24.500
When you killed her,

04:24.500 --> 04:26.230
you didn't even bat an eye.

04:28.380 --> 04:29.710
You've found out.

04:32.740 --> 04:33.820
My queen's crown

04:34.550 --> 04:36.110
will only be yours.

04:38.550 --> 04:39.790
You so-called love

04:41.670 --> 04:43.060
makes me sick.

04:45.230 --> 04:46.670
Here it is again, the same old look.

04:48.940 --> 04:49.780
Simu,

04:50.860 --> 04:52.230
the first time I saw you,

04:53.060 --> 04:54.260
I fell in love

04:54.590 --> 04:56.500
with your disdainful look.

04:56.940 --> 04:58.230
From then on,

04:58.790 --> 05:00.380
I could hardly forget that.

05:02.590 --> 05:04.180
But I don't like it

05:05.120 --> 05:05.990
when you look at me

05:05.990 --> 05:08.260
as if I were an ant!

05:31.860 --> 05:33.300
It fits you perfectly,

05:33.910 --> 05:34.940
my queen.

06:14.990 --> 06:15.830
Simu,

06:17.180 --> 06:19.300
I've spoiled you too much.

06:23.420 --> 06:24.260
Get out of here.

07:05.300 --> 07:06.140
I will

07:06.500 --> 07:07.740
have these things replaced.

07:09.590 --> 07:10.820
No matter how many you crush,

07:11.420 --> 07:12.550
I'll just have them replaced.

07:15.470 --> 07:16.310
No need.

07:18.350 --> 07:19.790
I don't like dead things.

08:45.310 --> 08:46.540
Why is His Lordship up there?

08:46.540 --> 08:47.500
Isn't it inappropriate?

08:48.790 --> 08:50.290
During Her Grace's seclusion,

08:50.780 --> 08:52.020
for the sake of convenience,

08:52.500 --> 08:53.340
from this day on,

08:53.830 --> 08:55.740
I'll be the acting sovereign.

08:56.140 --> 08:57.710
All of you shall obey my orders

08:57.990 --> 08:59.020
without fail.

09:00.540 --> 09:01.990
Does this come from Her Grace?

09:02.830 --> 09:03.710
Yes, Your Lordship.

09:04.020 --> 09:04.860
You...

09:05.740 --> 09:07.110
Yes, Your Lordship.

09:08.110 --> 09:10.110
Yes, Your Lordship.

09:14.950 --> 09:15.790
Your Lordship,

09:16.540 --> 09:17.990
the 24 Temples and the Ascension Pool

09:17.990 --> 09:19.020
have been searched.

09:19.380 --> 09:20.660
Jiang Ai hasn't been found.

09:21.350 --> 09:22.430
I've sent my men

09:22.620 --> 09:23.990
to search all the valleys.

09:24.380 --> 09:25.710
I believe we'll find her soon.

09:50.110 --> 09:50.990
You may leave too.

09:52.110 --> 09:53.500
Do I have the honor

09:54.110 --> 09:55.620
to ease your worries,

09:55.620 --> 09:56.460
Your Lordship?

10:03.740 --> 10:05.230
What do you think

10:06.070 --> 10:07.310
is a dead thing

10:08.140 --> 10:09.620
and what is a living thing?

10:12.140 --> 10:13.110
In my opinion,

10:14.710 --> 10:15.900
dead things are in the Void.

10:16.470 --> 10:17.310
Living things are

10:18.070 --> 10:18.990
in the Mortal World.

10:21.740 --> 10:23.070
This cup is originally

10:23.070 --> 10:24.310
from the Mortal World.

10:25.620 --> 10:27.260
Then why is it a dead thing

10:27.950 --> 10:29.540
in our world?

10:32.260 --> 10:33.230
Perhaps because

10:33.590 --> 10:35.110
it was never meant to belong here.

10:53.310 --> 10:54.310
Flowers for sale.

10:56.110 --> 10:56.990
Flowers.

10:58.860 --> 10:59.740
Flowers for sale.

11:00.740 --> 11:02.590
Flowers for sale.

11:04.380 --> 11:06.020
Miss, would you like some flowers?

11:06.260 --> 11:07.310
No, thank you.

11:09.350 --> 11:11.430
- Living things?
- Flowers.

11:41.830 --> 11:43.500
(The Void is a dead land.)

11:44.300 --> 11:45.140
(Earthly things)

11:45.140 --> 11:47.020
(can't survive here.)

11:48.500 --> 11:50.110
(But I'll force them.)

14:08.430 --> 14:09.270
It's done.

14:11.190 --> 14:12.110
Xu,

14:12.110 --> 14:13.070
get some rest early.

14:15.140 --> 14:15.980
I'm all right now.

14:17.110 --> 14:17.950
You should go to bed.

14:18.310 --> 14:19.610
- But...
- I'm fine now.

14:39.860 --> 14:40.700
(Back in Weizhou,)

14:41.780 --> 14:42.990
(we suffered heavy losses.)

14:44.540 --> 14:45.620
(I must make)

14:45.620 --> 14:46.460
(a new strategy)

14:47.380 --> 14:48.230
(to retake Weizhou)

14:49.380 --> 14:51.110
(and avenge our dead soldiers.)

14:55.070 --> 14:56.590
Chenying was right.

14:57.740 --> 14:58.860
Great Ancestor wouldn't want

14:58.860 --> 14:59.700
to see you like this.

15:07.890 --> 15:08.740
Luda has become

15:08.740 --> 15:09.710
the High Priest.

15:11.740 --> 15:13.190
I don't know how,

15:13.870 --> 15:14.710
but he made his army

15:14.710 --> 15:15.780
fearless of death.

15:17.780 --> 15:18.660
We're at a stalemate

15:18.660 --> 15:19.500
with them.

15:20.830 --> 15:22.110
My injury is no big deal.

15:23.620 --> 15:24.990
I examined the enemy's blood

15:25.230 --> 15:27.020
on Commandant Xia's weapon.

15:27.710 --> 15:29.110
I found out they were poisoned.

15:29.830 --> 15:31.780
With this poison in their wounds,

15:32.070 --> 15:33.470
the soldiers won't feel the pain

15:34.070 --> 15:35.590
and they'll fight until death.

15:38.540 --> 15:39.430
Luda used poison

15:39.430 --> 15:40.660
to manipulate his soldiers.

15:43.710 --> 15:45.710
What a great cost.

15:47.190 --> 15:48.030
To win this war,

15:48.900 --> 15:50.380
he has gone insane.

15:52.430 --> 15:54.110
We both have suffered losses.

15:54.380 --> 15:55.590
The war is deadlocked.

15:56.230 --> 15:57.380
Why don't you calm down

15:57.590 --> 15:58.430
and think carefully?

15:58.660 --> 15:59.950
Don't let panic take over,

16:00.140 --> 16:01.190
or you'll take the bait.

16:02.230 --> 16:03.660
If Great Ancestor returns

16:04.620 --> 16:05.620
and finds you dead,

16:06.230 --> 16:07.710
your future will be ruined.

16:07.860 --> 16:09.430
So will mine.

16:18.380 --> 16:19.900
What's happening with Simu?

16:23.540 --> 16:24.830
Something must be wrong with her.

16:27.110 --> 16:28.260
Still won't tell the truth?

16:30.540 --> 16:31.380
The Void...

16:35.500 --> 16:37.310
Something indeed happened there.

16:37.660 --> 16:38.620
But not very serious.

16:40.070 --> 16:41.430
If the Sovereign vanished,

16:41.950 --> 16:42.830
the Mortal World

16:42.830 --> 16:44.190
would definitely suffer.

16:44.620 --> 16:45.500
Great Ancestor

16:45.500 --> 16:46.710
wouldn't allow such a thing

16:46.710 --> 16:47.550
to happen.

16:48.990 --> 16:49.860
General Duan,

16:51.070 --> 16:53.110
you must stay alive.

16:53.660 --> 16:55.190
Before she comes back to you,

16:56.110 --> 16:57.660
you have to be alive.

17:04.630 --> 17:05.910
I must stay alive too.

17:07.060 --> 17:07.900
Let's go.

17:22.990 --> 17:23.830
(Simu,)

17:25.300 --> 17:26.190
(I await your return.)

18:10.700 --> 18:16.030
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

18:16.360 --> 18:20.610
♪Light encountered shadow♪

18:21.970 --> 18:27.340
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

18:27.640 --> 18:32.240
♪The unbreakable fate♪

18:33.330 --> 18:35.170
♪Suddenly cracked♪

18:47.420 --> 18:52.750
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

18:53.080 --> 18:57.330
♪Light encountered shadow♪

18:58.690 --> 19:04.060
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

19:04.360 --> 19:08.460
♪The unbreakable fate♪

19:08.460 --> 19:09.780
(Xiazhou)

19:09.780 --> 19:10.670
(Five years later,)

19:11.430 --> 19:13.060
(Duan Xu led the Liang Army)

19:13.390 --> 19:17.470
(to conquer Yingzhou, Tanzhou,
Ruzhou, and Mozhou.)

19:18.260 --> 19:21.060
(But heavy forces of the Chong Army)

19:21.540 --> 19:22.990
(still besieged them menacingly.)

19:33.380 --> 19:37.020
(Young Xue Chenying)

19:39.100 --> 19:42.260
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

19:42.260 --> 19:44.790
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

19:44.790 --> 19:50.310
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

19:50.310 --> 19:53.550
♪Following fate's guidance♪

19:53.550 --> 19:58.410
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

19:58.750 --> 20:01.770
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

20:02.920 --> 20:08.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

20:08.540 --> 20:12.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

20:14.240 --> 20:19.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

20:19.860 --> 20:23.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

20:25.570 --> 20:27.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

20:30.120 --> 20:33.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

20:33.280 --> 20:35.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

20:35.810 --> 20:41.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

20:41.330 --> 20:44.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

20:44.570 --> 20:49.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

20:49.770 --> 20:52.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

20:52.790 --> 20:55.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

20:55.870 --> 20:58.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

20:58.400 --> 21:03.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

21:03.990 --> 21:07.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

21:07.220 --> 21:12.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

21:12.330 --> 21:15.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

21:45.990 --> 21:46.990
It's almost time.

22:11.260 --> 22:12.100
Don't give me that look.

22:13.100 --> 22:14.100
I don't do this for you,

22:14.630 --> 22:15.630
but for Simu.

22:17.150 --> 22:18.100
Get better quickly.

22:21.870 --> 22:22.820
I've wanted to ask.

22:23.300 --> 22:24.260
Everyone in the Void

22:24.260 --> 22:25.470
wants to be the Sovereign.

22:26.630 --> 22:27.820
Why did you

22:28.990 --> 22:30.260
submit to He Simu?

22:37.430 --> 22:39.500
In the past 300 years under her reign,

22:40.430 --> 22:41.470
the Void has been the best

22:41.470 --> 22:42.670
I've ever seen.

22:43.580 --> 22:45.870
No one else can be a better sovereign.

22:51.540 --> 22:52.740
Since you told me

22:52.910 --> 22:54.150
what happened during her reign,

22:54.670 --> 22:55.630
I've been thinking.

22:56.740 --> 22:57.630
If I had managed

22:57.630 --> 22:58.670
to be the Sovereign,

22:59.340 --> 23:00.580
the Void under my reign...

23:02.990 --> 23:03.830
It might be

23:03.990 --> 23:05.300
as terrible as it is now.

23:10.870 --> 23:11.870
The real sovereign should

23:12.630 --> 23:13.540
go back to the throne.

23:15.500 --> 23:17.020
Any news on the Left Token?

23:17.740 --> 23:18.740
Haven't found it yet.

23:21.190 --> 23:23.580
What about Jiang Ai and Bai Sanxing?

23:24.100 --> 23:24.940
Still searching.

23:25.780 --> 23:26.670
It's been five years.

23:27.190 --> 23:28.780
You haven't even found two spirits!

23:30.820 --> 23:31.660
Your Lordship,

23:31.950 --> 23:32.820
as long as Jiang Ai

23:32.820 --> 23:33.780
still holds the Token,

23:34.430 --> 23:35.300
we can't open

23:35.300 --> 23:36.430
the spirit stone storehouse

23:36.870 --> 23:37.910
to get any stones out.

23:38.870 --> 23:40.230
She's been hiding for five years.

23:40.740 --> 23:41.580
Our spirit stones

23:41.820 --> 23:42.870
are almost used up.

23:43.500 --> 23:44.340
And yesterday,

23:44.340 --> 23:45.710
a large number of spirits gathered.

23:46.190 --> 23:47.300
They attacked the 24 Temples

23:47.300 --> 23:48.140
and ransacked them.

23:49.260 --> 23:50.100
Luckily, I led my men

23:50.670 --> 23:51.510
to execute them.

23:53.470 --> 23:54.670
Outside the Sovereign's Hall,

23:54.990 --> 23:56.190
chaos has been everywhere.

23:56.820 --> 23:57.660
That's right.

24:15.740 --> 24:16.580
Your Lordship,

24:16.780 --> 24:17.780
we located Jiang Ai.

24:26.740 --> 24:28.980
(Ascension Pool)

24:40.580 --> 24:41.430
Yan Ke,

24:42.390 --> 24:43.540
since you're here,

24:44.100 --> 24:45.390
why don't you come out?

24:49.950 --> 24:51.150
Give me the Left Token

24:51.740 --> 24:53.500
and I'll let you leave the Void.

24:55.100 --> 24:56.820
I don't want to be hunted down

24:57.190 --> 24:59.340
by the Starhaven Sect
in the Mortal World.

24:59.740 --> 25:00.820
Then you stay here

25:00.820 --> 25:01.950
and get annihilated!

25:17.150 --> 25:17.990
Yan Ke,

25:18.500 --> 25:19.910
how dare you appear before me?

25:22.580 --> 25:24.430
Does Simu know you brought out

25:25.820 --> 25:26.870
your old lover?

25:27.820 --> 25:29.670
Let me ask you this.

25:30.500 --> 25:32.780
If Simu finds out

25:32.780 --> 25:34.670
you killed her father,

25:35.340 --> 25:36.820
what will you do?

25:39.390 --> 25:40.230
What...

25:52.670 --> 25:54.580
You even killed your own kind.

25:55.100 --> 25:56.430
You're really merciless.

25:57.540 --> 25:58.580
It was you

25:58.580 --> 26:00.150
who killed He Simu's father.

26:00.580 --> 26:02.630
But you stayed by her side deceitfully

26:03.020 --> 26:04.060
and asked her to kill me,

26:04.060 --> 26:05.300
the only witness to the truth.

26:05.710 --> 26:07.150
If He Simu finds out,

26:09.670 --> 26:11.300
she'll tear you apart.

26:12.780 --> 26:14.910
That's why you were so nervous.

26:15.670 --> 26:16.540
So you weren't scared

26:16.540 --> 26:18.150
that Bai Sanxing would find you.

26:18.710 --> 26:20.150
You were scared

26:20.150 --> 26:21.870
that Her Grace would know the truth

26:22.020 --> 26:23.870
after she met with Bai Sanxing.

26:24.260 --> 26:25.990
You talk too much.

26:33.580 --> 26:34.740
300 years ago,

26:34.740 --> 26:36.190
I might have feared you.

26:36.630 --> 26:37.580
But being stuck in there

26:37.580 --> 26:38.710
for that long

26:39.260 --> 26:40.910
has left you far weaker than before.

27:02.670 --> 27:03.510
Leave.

27:10.380 --> 27:12.700
(Left)

27:16.260 --> 27:17.950
You can't get away.

27:19.300 --> 27:20.820
The whole Void

27:21.670 --> 27:24.060
will soon be mine.

27:59.260 --> 28:00.100
Simu,

28:01.100 --> 28:02.300
I suddenly remembered.

28:02.990 --> 28:03.870
Today is the day

28:03.870 --> 28:05.230
we first met 300 years ago.

28:05.950 --> 28:07.500
We should celebrate this anniversary.

28:11.430 --> 28:12.500
That day, as I remember,

28:12.990 --> 28:14.300
thousands of spirits rebelled.

28:14.820 --> 28:16.060
You held the Kunwu Blade

28:16.430 --> 28:18.260
to suppress them alone.

28:19.630 --> 28:21.060
That was the first time I saw you.

28:22.260 --> 28:23.740
You were shining brilliantly.

28:25.230 --> 28:26.070
Simu,

28:27.100 --> 28:28.230
you always say

28:28.230 --> 28:29.820
I want supreme power.

28:30.910 --> 28:31.750
You are wrong.

28:32.390 --> 28:33.470
I want both,

28:34.630 --> 28:35.470
you and power.

28:37.580 --> 28:39.340
Without you, I couldn't

28:39.340 --> 28:40.430
govern the Void well.

28:40.910 --> 28:41.750
Without you,

28:43.950 --> 28:45.710
everything would be meaningless.

28:57.670 --> 28:58.670
Today really is a day

28:58.670 --> 28:59.990
worth celebrating.

29:01.440 --> 29:02.300
300 years ago,

29:02.300 --> 29:03.670
my father suddenly died.

29:05.190 --> 29:06.150
I had no choice

29:07.260 --> 29:08.500
but to take over the Void.

29:15.870 --> 29:16.820
And today,

29:19.740 --> 29:21.580
I'll kill the one
who murdered my father.

29:39.340 --> 29:41.950
You... You know that?

29:44.260 --> 29:46.060
I heard what you said

29:46.950 --> 29:48.340
on the Void Mountain.

30:08.100 --> 30:09.630
I've done a lot of things these years.

30:09.630 --> 30:11.060
This is the only thing

30:11.870 --> 30:13.300
I never want you to know.

30:14.950 --> 30:16.820
Back then, I wanted to be the Sovereign.

30:16.820 --> 30:18.190
So I had no choice

30:18.190 --> 30:19.740
but to kill him.

30:21.260 --> 30:22.500
But for your sake,

30:23.300 --> 30:24.300
I've been the Right Hand

30:24.300 --> 30:25.580
over the past 300 years

30:25.580 --> 30:27.020
and never complained!

30:29.190 --> 30:31.150
Yet you still don't accept me.

30:32.500 --> 30:34.580
So I have to lock you here.

30:39.300 --> 30:40.190
But all these things

30:40.190 --> 30:41.470
no longer matter.

30:42.540 --> 30:43.380
Simu,

30:44.500 --> 30:45.910
I'll make it up to you.

30:47.300 --> 30:48.580
You love the Mortal World, right?

30:49.260 --> 30:51.100
I wouldn't mind uniting

30:51.100 --> 30:52.100
the two worlds.

30:52.820 --> 30:54.150
Wherever you want to go,

30:54.430 --> 30:55.500
I'll go there with you.

30:57.060 --> 30:58.670
Just don't leave me.

31:02.870 --> 31:04.020
You killed my father.

31:07.880 --> 31:08.740
Does it

31:08.740 --> 31:10.230
really matter that much?

31:12.190 --> 31:13.740
If I hadn't killed him,

31:14.500 --> 31:15.500
would things be different

31:15.500 --> 31:16.780
between us?

31:18.820 --> 31:20.020
There's no if!

31:49.260 --> 31:50.300
This is where your father

31:50.300 --> 31:52.060
established the Golden-wall Decrees.

31:54.540 --> 31:56.100
You want to avenge him, don't you?

31:57.670 --> 31:59.260
Then let's end this

31:59.540 --> 32:00.630
right here and now.

33:30.150 --> 33:30.990
Stop the pursuit.

33:32.150 --> 33:33.230
That was my oversight.

33:34.740 --> 33:36.100
He pretended to fight me

33:36.540 --> 33:37.740
just to grab the Glazed Pagoda

33:38.260 --> 33:39.780
to hide his aura and make his escape.

33:40.990 --> 33:42.430
He's out of reach now.

34:19.100 --> 34:20.430
You were expelled from the Void?

34:28.540 --> 34:29.540
Who allowed you

34:29.540 --> 34:31.060
to talk to me like this?

34:33.620 --> 34:34.870
You came here

34:34.870 --> 34:36.020
to seek my help, didn't you?

34:37.270 --> 34:38.110
Help?

34:39.100 --> 34:40.020
You don't deserve it.

34:41.270 --> 34:42.430
In that case,

34:43.310 --> 34:44.350
I won't hold you back.

34:48.700 --> 34:50.700
You're merely a pawn.

34:51.660 --> 34:52.950
I can give you power,

34:53.270 --> 34:55.220
and I can take it back anytime.

34:56.140 --> 34:57.700
You'd better get that straight.

34:59.060 --> 35:00.750
Don't think being the High Priest

35:01.100 --> 35:02.830
means you have nothing to worry about.

35:04.140 --> 35:06.180
If the North Chong falls,

35:06.700 --> 35:08.950
you'll perish with it too.

35:18.790 --> 35:20.700
Duan Xu never loses a battle

35:21.430 --> 35:23.750
simply because he has a pact
with the Sovereign.

35:24.950 --> 35:26.470
No wonder in Youzhou,

35:27.430 --> 35:29.790
his power was unmatched.

35:30.910 --> 35:31.750
That's right.

35:34.310 --> 35:36.020
The Sovereign is back on the throne.

35:36.910 --> 35:39.220
The course of the war will be affected.

35:43.220 --> 35:44.100
What should I do?

35:46.660 --> 35:47.660
When I'm around,

35:48.390 --> 35:49.950
you will succeed.

35:51.830 --> 35:54.470
All you have to do is follow my orders.

36:10.310 --> 36:11.270
Simu,

36:11.270 --> 36:12.430
you're finally back.

36:28.020 --> 36:28.860
Bai Sanxing,

36:30.790 --> 36:32.060
what are your plans for future?

36:33.430 --> 36:34.500
Will you still fight me

36:34.500 --> 36:35.620
for the throne?

36:39.390 --> 36:40.230
It depends.

36:40.910 --> 36:41.870
300 years ago,

36:41.870 --> 36:42.910
I rose against He Yicheng.

36:43.470 --> 36:44.350
Then now,

36:46.180 --> 36:47.060
I could do the same.

36:49.580 --> 36:50.420
I'll be waiting.

36:51.220 --> 36:52.180
Feel free to try.

36:57.020 --> 36:57.860
Back then,

36:58.060 --> 36:59.500
I naively believed Yan Ke.

37:32.370 --> 37:33.220
I thought he meant

37:33.220 --> 37:34.270
to help me,

37:34.500 --> 37:35.390
so he killed He Yicheng

37:35.950 --> 37:37.700
and spread rumors that he died for love.

37:38.990 --> 37:39.830
To my surprise,

37:40.180 --> 37:41.060
he then

37:41.470 --> 37:43.020
worked with you to trap me.

37:48.180 --> 37:49.580
Not until he and Jiang Ai

37:50.100 --> 37:51.350
lured me into the Prison

37:51.660 --> 37:53.060
and the three of you attacked me

37:53.580 --> 37:54.420
did I realize

37:54.950 --> 37:56.580
that everything was just his trap.

37:58.990 --> 37:59.830
Unfortunately,

38:00.950 --> 38:01.830
it was too late.

38:04.910 --> 38:05.950
I never believed

38:05.950 --> 38:06.990
my father died for love.

38:08.020 --> 38:09.500
You were arrogant and rebellious,

38:10.830 --> 38:12.220
but you never took advantage.

38:13.270 --> 38:14.470
If you had killed my father,

38:15.310 --> 38:16.830
you would have told everyone.

38:17.790 --> 38:20.390
You didn't need that excuse.

38:22.180 --> 38:23.140
I won't get over it

38:23.660 --> 38:25.270
until I capture Yan Ke.

38:28.390 --> 38:29.230
From this day,

38:31.580 --> 38:32.910
hunt down the traitor Yan Ke.

38:33.540 --> 38:34.870
Restart the curfew.

38:35.580 --> 38:36.540
Thoroughly investigate

38:36.550 --> 38:38.100
all riots over the past five years.

38:38.580 --> 38:39.910
Severely punish those who violated

38:41.180 --> 38:42.140
the Golden-wall Decrees.

38:43.990 --> 38:44.830
Yes.

38:48.990 --> 38:49.830
Move!

38:52.660 --> 38:54.100
Officer, I heard...

38:54.100 --> 38:55.350
Her Grace ended her seclusion

38:55.350 --> 38:56.390
and restarted the Decrees.

38:56.390 --> 38:57.390
Is that true, officer?

38:59.580 --> 39:00.830
Orders from Her Grace!

39:01.540 --> 39:02.660
Riots in the past five years

39:03.020 --> 39:04.180
will be investigated!

39:04.750 --> 39:06.100
- Excellent!
- Great!

39:06.100 --> 39:06.940
Move!

39:07.140 --> 39:07.980
This is great.

39:08.140 --> 39:09.060
Her Grace is back.

39:09.910 --> 39:11.430
I'm finally safe.

39:11.430 --> 39:12.270
Great!

39:12.470 --> 39:13.910
Her Grace is back!

39:16.540 --> 39:17.580
Awesome!

39:19.700 --> 39:21.910
The Left Token is back with me.

39:22.500 --> 39:23.910
The spirit stones have been

39:23.910 --> 39:24.870
orderly distributed.

39:26.540 --> 39:27.390
It's been five years.

39:27.400 --> 39:28.700
I'm so happy to see you

39:28.990 --> 39:29.910
safe and sound.

39:31.310 --> 39:32.150
It's been five years.

39:32.580 --> 39:34.180
You're still as exuberant

39:34.310 --> 39:35.150
as before.

39:35.540 --> 39:36.990
How I envy you.

39:37.750 --> 39:39.100
You faithless traitor.

39:39.520 --> 39:40.390
For five years,

39:40.390 --> 39:41.470
you worked for Yan Ke

39:41.470 --> 39:42.950
and lived quite a prosperous life!

39:43.100 --> 39:44.100
How could you still come?

39:49.100 --> 39:50.140
Under Your Grace's orders,

39:50.580 --> 39:52.390
I went undercover with Yan Ke.

39:55.060 --> 39:56.020
He...

39:56.020 --> 39:57.910
It's the evidence of the violation

39:58.430 --> 40:00.310
of some lords who submitted to Yan Ke.

40:01.310 --> 40:02.220
Please see the truth.

40:03.140 --> 40:05.140
So you weren't loyal to him,

40:05.620 --> 40:06.660
but worked as a spy?

40:07.500 --> 40:08.580
Of course I wasn't loyal.

40:09.020 --> 40:10.020
I endured all these years

40:11.140 --> 40:12.060
just for this day

40:12.220 --> 40:13.060
when Her Grace returned

40:13.270 --> 40:14.110
and set things right.

40:16.180 --> 40:17.430
What a surprise, Yun.

40:17.580 --> 40:18.620
You pretended so perfectly.

40:18.870 --> 40:20.380
For all these years, I misjudged you.

40:20.580 --> 40:22.060
Come on, I'll kowtow to you.

40:22.390 --> 40:23.350
Hey, Leiqi.

40:23.350 --> 40:24.190
It doesn't matter.

40:26.830 --> 40:28.390
We all work for Her Grace.

40:36.430 --> 40:37.310
You may rise.

40:39.340 --> 40:40.180
Thank you.

40:40.180 --> 40:41.020
This is great.

40:41.350 --> 40:42.540
Her Grace is back.

40:43.100 --> 40:44.910
The Void will be back to normal.

40:45.720 --> 40:46.620
So this is how

40:46.620 --> 40:47.620
they have a meeting now.

40:48.540 --> 40:49.380
Interesting.

40:50.940 --> 40:54.940
(Liang)

40:55.310 --> 40:56.870
Deliver the intel to Wu Shengliu.

41:25.710 --> 41:31.570
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

41:32.200 --> 41:37.710
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

41:38.300 --> 41:44.310
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

41:45.400 --> 41:50.010
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

41:52.140 --> 41:53.620
It's been five years!

41:53.620 --> 41:54.830
Do you know how worried he is?

41:54.830 --> 41:55.670
You...

41:57.780 --> 42:03.400
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

42:03.930 --> 42:07.290
♪There are passions and pains♪

42:07.490 --> 42:10.390
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

42:11.070 --> 42:17.300
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

42:18.610 --> 42:21.370
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

42:21.370 --> 42:23.020
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

42:23.020 --> 42:25.850
♪What would come of it?♪

42:26.260 --> 42:27.760
♪I care for no one but you♪

42:27.760 --> 42:29.410
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

42:29.410 --> 42:32.590
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

42:33.110 --> 42:35.800
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

42:35.800 --> 42:38.550
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

42:38.790 --> 42:41.150
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

42:41.150 --> 42:45.120
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

42:57.620 --> 42:58.460
Simu,

42:59.500 --> 43:00.430
is it really you?

43:01.470 --> 43:02.500
Are you really here?

43:03.870 --> 43:04.710
It's me.

43:05.040 --> 43:09.890
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

43:09.910 --> 43:11.390
I summoned you many times.

43:14.020 --> 43:14.860
I know.

43:18.220 --> 43:19.060
But you didn't come.

43:22.100 --> 43:23.270
Now, I've come.

43:24.600 --> 43:29.700
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

43:29.820 --> 43:31.680
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

43:31.680 --> 43:33.290
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

43:33.290 --> 43:36.140
♪What would come of it?♪

43:36.660 --> 43:38.100
♪I care for no one but you♪

43:38.100 --> 43:39.750
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

43:39.750 --> 43:43.000
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

43:43.420 --> 43:46.030
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

43:47.100 --> 43:47.940
I'm all right.

43:49.080 --> 43:51.490
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

43:51.490 --> 43:55.500
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

44:00.180 --> 44:01.270
Never before had I been

44:01.270 --> 44:02.220
that restless.

44:03.750 --> 44:04.870
I couldn't reach you.

44:06.540 --> 44:08.310
And I didn't know what was happening.

44:11.620 --> 44:12.460
Don't worry.

44:14.700 --> 44:16.180
If anything had happened to me,

44:17.220 --> 44:18.350
you would have known.

44:20.060 --> 44:21.750
If I had been annihilated,

44:22.750 --> 44:24.430
the world would have fallen into chaos

44:25.540 --> 44:26.750
and disasters would have raged.

44:41.440 --> 44:46.770
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

44:47.100 --> 44:51.350
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:52.710 --> 44:58.080
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:58.380 --> 45:02.980
♪The unbreakable fate♪

45:04.070 --> 45:05.910
♪Suddenly cracked♪

45:18.120 --> 45:23.560
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

45:23.740 --> 45:28.070
♪Light encountered shadow♪

45:29.440 --> 45:34.830
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

45:35.060 --> 45:39.000
♪The unbreakable fate♪

45:40.770 --> 45:42.660
♪Suddenly cracked♪

45:45.320 --> 45:48.480
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

45:48.480 --> 45:51.010
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

45:51.010 --> 45:56.530
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

45:56.530 --> 45:59.770
♪Following fate's guidance♪

45:59.770 --> 46:04.630
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

46:04.970 --> 46:07.990
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

46:07.990 --> 46:10.810
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

46:11.070 --> 46:13.600
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

46:13.600 --> 46:19.020
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

46:19.190 --> 46:22.260
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

46:22.420 --> 46:27.320
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

46:27.530 --> 46:31.000
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
